{"tid":1593624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係台灣讀書，返工嘅香港人同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-25T07:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T15:50:10.000Z","uid":45228,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7bca42210a0c1cb946ceea98535838b93af23269","tid":1593624,"uid":45228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"我係一個係台灣讀書嘅香港人，8月9月頭返咗台灣，令到我無辦法每晚十點大叫，又無得係商場同大家合唱，最重要係無得同各位手足出去發夢。<br />\n我相信好多係台灣讀書嘅香港人都有我以上嘅心情，但係929我哋有機會啦，雖然唔係香港，但可以係台灣隔海聲援，我希望929可以係台灣同咁多位在台港人一齊唱願榮光歸香港。<br />\n929係台灣不見不散"},{"pid":"2f8a60daed678d0f45abfc6cae0c26cdb23ae0b2","tid":1593624,"uid":33459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3439ed676999eb985b3e2531da82d78ce1e509a","tid":1593624,"uid":53352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"不如諗下點幫係大學入面被支那人恰既手足"},{"pid":"af5f46fb5841edd6b1f21c9730d511d6d973f48c","tid":1593624,"uid":33459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnjDBbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnjDBbm.jpg&h=56d7ed15&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFshRKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFshRKH.jpg&h=d16c3352&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9efe96844055674d79fd14d97d23bee2ec13e88","tid":1593624,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:05:20.000Z","msg":"大家要記住呀！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">929反赤納粹行動</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全球呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n我地唔可以輸比世界上任何一個地區，我地幾咁憎赤納粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\